tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE DynamicProgrammingResults (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    subproblem_name VARCHAR(255),
    result_value INT
)

CREATE TABLE Subproblems (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    subproblem_name VARCHAR(255),
    parent_subproblem_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE SubproblemDependencies (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    subproblem_id INT,
    dependent_subproblem_id INT
)
